transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan good morning sir, main Vinit kar raha hun sir IndiaMART se.
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Haan sir kaise hain sir?
Customer: Badhiya ji sir aap sunaiye.
Executive: Main bhi badhiya hun sir, thank you.
Executive: Sir kal aapne call kiya tha sir bataiye kya issue aa rahi hai sir.
Customer: Sir mera issue ye aa raha hai ki mere buyleads mein hai na ek mini slitting rewinding machine ki inquiry jyada aa rahi hai. Baki meri jo slitting machines hai unki inquiry aa hi nahi rahi bilkul mere paas.
Executive: Ek minute sir aap call pe rahiye main check kar leta hun.
Customer: Haan ek baar mere check kar lijiye please.

Executive: Palit sir bol rahe hai na sir?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Palit sir bol rahe hai na ye 12 minute.
Customer: Achha buyleads buyleads.
Executive: Okay.
Executive: Iski jyada inquiry aa rahi hai? Kaun se machine ki?
Customer: Mini slitting rewinding machine ki mere paas jyada aa rahi hai jabki mere ko sahi chahiye coating machine aur slitting rewinding machine ki inquiry mere ko jyada chahiye.
Executive: Okay.
Customer: Haan mini wale ki chhoti wale ki aa rahi hai isliye koi isme profit margin hai hi nahi to mere ko koi fayda nahi kam tarike se iska. Haan matlab aati rahe kabhi kabhi mil jaye to thik hai.
Executive: Ek minute main dekh leta hun kitna iski buyleads aa rahi hai.


Executive: Slitting rewinding machine ki jyada aa rahi hai coating machine ki nahi aa rahi hai.
Customer: Haan coating machine ki bilkul bhi nahi aa rahi ji kai din se nahi aa rahi coating machine ki. Aap ek jankari karwao.
Executive: Ek baar dekh leta hun ki sir ye IndiaMART pe hi buyleads generate ho rahi hai ki nahi coating machine ki ek baar main isko check kar leta hun aap call pe rahiye sir.
Customer: Haan ek baar check kar lijiye.


Executive: Sir aapka elastic tape making machine nahi ho gaya na coating machine nahi ho gaya na sir?
Customer: Nahi nahi elastic tape machine alag alag hi hum banate nahi elastic tape machine.
Executive: Achha ye warning tape executor tape nahi hai to ye export ka hai.
Executive: Kaun si?
Executive: Sir export ka main jo aapko leads hai na coating machine ke sir export ka hai. Main abhi import ka dekh raha hun export matlab wo bahar ka hai. Main ek baar dekh raha hun sir yahan ka.



Executive: Sir main ki jaise ki abhi check kar raha hun sir jo IndiaMART pe jo lead aati hai na sir coating machine ki abhi lead hi nahi hai sir IndiaMART pe hi lead.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Aa hi nahi rahi hai nahi IndiaMART pe abhi nahi aa rahi hai filhal.
Customer: Slitting rewinding machine?
Executive: Ek minute main batata hun.

Executive: Slitting rewinding machine.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan main dekh leta hun.

Executive: Haan ek sir lead hai iska but wo yahan ka nahi hai sir wo France ka lead hai.
Customer: Achha. India mein generate hi nahi ho rahi kya abhi ye lead.
Executive: Generate hoti hai matlab aisa nahi ki sir compulsory nahi ki daily basis pe generate hoti hai agar matlab jaise main dekh pa raha hun matlab 24 ghante ke andar mein koi generate nahi hua hai leads.
Customer: Achha.
Executive: Sir kyunki yahan pe hum log ka ek site hota hai jo IndiaMART pe jitni bhi category ka lead generate hoti hai na wo hum log check karte hain. Jaise ki main jo main portal jo IndiaMART pe hi hoti hai wahan pe main dono machine ka check kiya hun coating machine ka bhi aur rewinding machine ka bhi. Coating machine ka jo maine ek bataya tha jo aap bol rahe the ki deal nahi karte hain wo tha aur sir ek do coating machine hai jo Oman aur Bangladesh ka desh ka hai to wo to sir export ho gaya aap to deal karte hain domestic mein. Aur ek sir main dekh raha hun butter paper rewinding machine with printing ka ek leads hai thik hai 11 ghante pehle ka wo sir France ka lead hai. Wo capacity upto one ton per day chahiye.
Executive: To jaise hi sir aapko domestic lead hogi to sir jarur aapke paas aayegi isliye maine check kar liya agar sir yahan pe agar lead aa raha to aapke paas bhi nahi aa raha hota to main fir isko backend pe check karwata ki kya issue hai aapke profile mein ki nahi aa rahi hai but sir wo main IndiaMART pe nahi aa rahi hai isliye sir aapke paas nahi aa raha hai.
Customer: Thik hai ji.
Executive: Hai na sir okay okay.
Customer: Okay thank you.
